snippet.title: Character Demo - "Navia: Unofficial Operation" | Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
Although the Spina di Rosula operates efficiently, the results achieved are often proportional to the ruckus caused.
Occasionally, when the scene gets out of control, a Melusine officer would hurriedly step in to intervene by stating "Now, now, everyone, please, don't panic. They're just filming the latest crime movie!"
